| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3745 — Recovery Inhibition (kazu)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: df3c6a52-7b49-570d-8fcf-a3422bf8cf37"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
